{"tid":1509670,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[集思廣益]國泰員工正被白色恐怖濃罩，人人自危，入黎比D支持佢地！","createTime":"2019-08-27T02:19:35.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-27T14:30:36.000Z","uid":116788,"like":34,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"2ef4463abcf3fc6b0e89520e495ed118342f75d5","tid":1509670,"uid":116788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T02:19:35.000Z","msg":"國泰員工一直都好敢企出黎支持大家，而且好多為左香港出錢出力，<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n依家公司赤化染紅，清算一浪接一浪，內部濃罩白色恐怖，<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n每位員工都擔心自己係下一個比人篤灰清算既人。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n大家坐埋一條船，集思廣益下有咩行動可以幫到佢地同支持到佢地。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n另外不妨比個<strong>正評</strong>佢地，正能量心靈上支持下，<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n比佢地知道就算係咁黑暗既時刻，佢地都唔係自己一個獨自去走依條路。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"943c949a1cff2467d9ebbca328a1e95a4296a575","tid":1509670,"uid":33930,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T02:20:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9hjf7rg.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9hjf7rg.gif&h=994c84f5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n九月一號下午一點機場見<br />\n<br />\n901機場和你塞 Channel<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyou&d=D7ApRvRekvrpuPbHHlYQrqpJ2kzo9njAZIZZFH2Kh%2FI%3D&h=21955446\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/stuckwithyou</a><br />\n901機場和你塞 公海<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyouopen\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyouopen&d=D7ApRvRekvrpuPbHHlYQrqpJ2kzo9njAZIZZFH2Kh%2FI%3D&h=489501ea\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/stuckwithyouopen</a><br />\n901機場和你塞 宣傳<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyoupromote\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me